      <scopecontent id="aspace_c5b08e241c2723d3b23d4f398e85e208">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The materials consists of photographs taken following the construction (and before the opening) of Sterling Memorial Library at Yale. Included are interior and exterior views, photographs of floor plans, friezes, archways, and window details.</p>  
